title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 §§ 197-3.18 - Registration period

N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 §§ 197-3.18 - Registration period

State Regulations

Each registration or renewal period for approved programs
or courses shall be for 12 months or a part thereof, said period to commence on

January 1st or date thereafter and to continue until December
31st. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19
§§
197-3.18

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
